tional cooperation and networking activities carried out in", "connection with the funded research.", "Swiss applicants may not apply for their own salaries.", "Partners from may be included as project partners article 11, Myanmar, Lao PDR and Cambodia", "paragraph 2 of the SNSF Funding Regulations on mySNF, under the condition that the partners from", "these countries provide their personnel costs / work effort in kind. The costs should correspond to no", "more than 20% of the overall Swiss budget.", "Submission", "Swiss applicants must submit an application via the online submission system mySNF for the same", "submitted. Please select the \u201cProgrammes / Southeast Asia deadline as the consortium applications are", "\u2013 Europe Joint Funding Scheme\u201d funding instrument.", "According to the SNSF policy on Open Research Data (follow this link for details), Swiss applicants must", "submit a Data Management Plan.", "For more information, please contact:", "Andrea Landolt", "Swiss National Science Foundation", "andrea.landolt@snf.ch", "+41 31 308 24 09", "1"], "bbox": [[0.504855, 0.098696, -0.005348000000000019, 0.018122], [0.315746, 0.113844, 0.377755, 0.018056], [0.071558, 0.146703, 0.839888, 0.018017], [0.071558, 0.161811, 0.8451909999999999, 0.018017], [0.071558, 0.176777, 0.558774, 0.018017], [0.071558, 0.209482, 0.08222700000000001, 0.018056], [0.071558, 0.233504, 0.8574029999999999, 0.018017], [0.071558, 0.24847, 0.857364, 0.018017], [0.071558, 0.263436, 0.7497050000000001, 0.018017], [0.071558, 0.295322, 0.169535, 0.018056], [0.071558, 0.327183, 0.857232, 0.018017], [0.071558, 0.344429, 0.341157, 0.018017], [0.13207, 0.37992, 0.757177, 0.018017], [0.162306, 0.397166, 0.34528299999999995, 0.018017], [0.13207, 0.415267, 0.7479140000000001, 0.018017], [0.162306, 0.432656, 0.696366, 0.018017], [0.162306, 0.449903, 0.641886, 0.018017], [0.13207, 0.468004, 0.773432, 0.018017], [0.13207, 0.486272, 0.74138, 0.018017], [0.162306, 0.503518, 0.07710899999999998, 